            | 
            a(href="#" target="_blank").footer__link Diana Vitanyi.
    div.footer__contact
        h3.header__tertiary--light Vragen? Stuur ons een bericht!
        form(id="contact_form").footer__form
            label(for="email") E-mailadres:
            input(type="email" name="email" id="contact_email" placeholder="voorbeeld@email.com" required)
            label(for="message") Bericht: 
            textarea(name="message", cols="30", rows="5" placeholder="Uw bericht..." maxlength="500" id="contact_message" required)
            button(type="submit" value="submit").btn.footer__cta.margin-bottom-medium verzenden